---
const socialLinks = [
    {
        name: 'Facebook',
        icon: 'f',
        url: 'https://www.facebook.com/gdgportugal',
    },
    {
        name: 'LinkedIn',
        icon: 'in',
        url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gdg-portugal',
    },
    {
        name: 'Twitter',
        icon: '𝕏',
        url: 'https://twitter.com/gdgportugal',
    },
    {
        name: 'Instagram',
        icon: '📷',
        url: 'https://www.instagram.com/gdgportugal',
    },
];
---

<section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div
            class="text-center mb-12"
        >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #202124;">
                Segue-nos nas Redes Sociais
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #5F6368;">
                Mantém-te atualizado com as últimas novidades, eventos e conteúdos da comunidade GDG Portugal
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6"
        >
            {socialLinks.map((social) => (
                <a
                    href={social.url}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center justify-center group hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 transition-all duration-300 text-2xl hover:scale-110 hover:rotate-5"
                        style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #111111, #1c1c1e, #004d40);"
                    >
                        <span class="text-white">{social.icon}</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 transition-colors duration-300" style="color: #202124;">
                        {social.name}
                    </h3>

                    <p class="text-sm text-center" style="color: #5F6368;">
                        Segue-nos no {social.name}
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="mt-4 px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 text-white hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-105"
                        style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #111111, #1c1c1e, #004d40);"
                    >
                        Seguir
                    </div>
                </a>
            ))}
        </div>

        <div
            class="mt-12 text-center"
        >
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #5F6368;">
                Junta-te à nossa comunidade e partilha as tuas experiências connosco!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
